cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and image processing, specifically the problem of height estimation from a single monocular remote sensing image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of the estimated height map for instance segmentation of buildings could also relate to cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.RO (Robotics).
